Here is a complete set of **35 questions on Functions in Python 3**, covering function definitions, arguments, scope, return values, recursion, lambdas, and integration with **list comprehensions** + **other ways of traversing/iterating lists** (for loops, while, enumerate, zip, map, filter, etc.).

Divided into three difficulty levels (10 each) + 5 Code Quality questions.

